1
00:02:41,771 --> 00:02:43,331
'Children are humans too.'

2
00:02:44,014 --> 00:02:46,687
'They are innocent and truthful
than elders.'

3
00:02:47,896 --> 00:02:51,571
'They don't have a wall of cunningness
around them.'

4
00:02:52,063 --> 00:02:54,421
'For their betterment we need...

5
00:02:55,303 --> 00:02:57,304
...to educate them in school...

6
00:02:58,093 --> 00:03:00,795
...they should get such a world...

7
00:03:01,530 --> 00:03:03,850
...where's there's love and affection.'

8
00:03:05,281 --> 00:03:06,979
'Guru Ravindranath Tagore.'

9
00:03:07,695 --> 00:03:14,455
"Beloved is in every color of heart."

10
00:03:15,510 --> 00:03:22,393
"He is very stone hearted."

11
00:03:23,289 --> 00:03:30,356
"The color of henna."

12
00:03:31,018 --> 00:03:37,302
"Beloved has gone abroad."

13
00:03:38,126 --> 00:03:45,167
"He hasn't sent any letter."

14
00:03:46,316 --> 00:03:54,573
"How can I live without you?"

15
00:03:56,078 --> 00:03:58,024
(Horn blares)

16
00:03:58,934 --> 00:04:02,969
Come here... Come on. Come here...

17
00:04:09,725 --> 00:04:11,360
Where is Dulari Devi School?

18
00:04:13,045 --> 00:04:16,454
Take a left turn and then a right turn...

19
00:04:16,705 --> 00:04:17,963
...you'll find a well...

20
00:04:18,098 --> 00:04:20,171
...the Dulari Devi School is
just opposite to it.

21
00:04:20,224 --> 00:04:22,766
Do you belong to the same village?
-We belong to the same school.

22
00:04:22,859 --> 00:04:25,036
Is it? Will you take me there?

23
00:04:25,061 --> 00:04:27,130
In your car?
-Yes.

24
00:04:27,996 --> 00:04:29,793
Sit inside. Come on.

25
00:04:45,140 --> 00:04:46,802
Tell me your names.

26
00:04:46,882 --> 00:04:47,940
Avdesh.
-Hari.

27
00:04:48,112 --> 00:04:48,868
Gorak.

28
00:04:49,206 --> 00:04:50,349
My name is Neha.

29
00:04:53,173 --> 00:04:54,376
Don't you have school today?

30
00:04:54,456 --> 00:04:57,048
I have, but I don't go.
-Why?

31
00:04:57,727 --> 00:04:59,700
The master is very shrew.

32
00:04:59,780 --> 00:05:01,194
He thrashes us badly.

33
00:05:01,714 --> 00:05:04,214
Hereafter, you have to
go to school every day.

34
00:05:05,389 --> 00:05:08,335
I have come to build
a big school in your village.

35
00:05:08,415 --> 00:05:09,346
Is it?

36
00:05:14,940 --> 00:05:16,331
Will you drink water?

37
00:05:16,997 --> 00:05:18,147
Here.

38
00:05:39,685 --> 00:05:42,215
It is fun to sit your car.

39
00:05:42,236 --> 00:05:44,658
Where's the cool breeze coming from?

40
00:05:44,969 --> 00:05:46,071
From here.

41
00:05:47,328 --> 00:05:52,124
(Laughs)

42
00:05:52,204 --> 00:05:56,145
Stop the car... drop us here...
drop us here.

43
00:05:57,861 --> 00:06:00,239
You'll find the school ahead.
We're going.

44
00:06:00,319 --> 00:06:02,740
How does it open? Tell me.

45
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:04,929
It opened. Let's go.
-Hey, stop.

46
00:06:07,095 --> 00:06:10,104
Let's go. Let's go.
-Hey, come on out.

47
00:06:12,486 --> 00:06:13,283
Avdesh.

48
00:06:22,687 --> 00:06:24,541
Do you want chocolates?

49
00:06:26,486 --> 00:06:27,931
Wait, I'll come.

50
00:06:34,119 --> 00:06:34,955
Come.

51
00:06:42,759 --> 00:06:44,721
Is it for me?
-Yes, it is for you.

52
00:06:45,315 --> 00:06:47,635
Give me one.
-Okay, I'll give you.

53
00:06:49,277 --> 00:06:52,144
This is for you and this for you.

54
00:06:54,841 --> 00:06:56,888
Chocolates.
-Yes.

55
00:06:57,991 --> 00:06:59,528
You also have one.

56
00:07:00,547 --> 00:07:02,810
Here are some books for you.

57
00:07:04,423 --> 00:07:07,019
Take a left and you'll find the school.
-Let's go.

58
00:07:07,617 --> 00:07:08,332
Hey?

59
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:17,023
Hey, look... the car is so nice.

60
00:07:17,103 --> 00:07:19,767
2 x 2 = 4!
-It is so nice.

61
00:07:19,997 --> 00:07:23,019
I think someone has come.
-2 x 3 = 6.

62
00:07:24,213 --> 00:07:26,723
Where's the headmaster? Let's go.

63
00:07:27,049 --> 00:07:33,741
(Indistinct chatter)

64
00:07:33,821 --> 00:07:35,120
She is going in.

65
00:07:36,038 --> 00:07:38,308
2 x 7 = 14.

66
00:07:39,376 --> 00:07:41,092
Greetings.
-Greetings.

67
00:07:41,172 --> 00:07:43,538
Who do you want to meet?
-I want to meet the headmaster.

68
00:07:43,889 --> 00:07:45,578
He is having bath. Look there.

69
00:07:45,794 --> 00:07:47,942
Hail Goddess Ganges!
Hail Goddess Ganges!

70
00:07:50,143 --> 00:07:52,981
Hail Goddess Ganges!
Hail Goddess Ganges!

71
00:07:53,535 --> 00:07:54,357
Come, let's go.

72
00:07:54,511 --> 00:07:57,592
Hey children, go to your classrooms!
-Let's go.

73
00:07:58,019 --> 00:08:00,113
They are children of this village...
come on.

74
00:08:01,582 --> 00:08:03,042
Come, please have a seat.

75
00:08:03,527 --> 00:08:06,903
You sit here and I'll
call the headmaster.

76
00:08:06,983 --> 00:08:08,419
Have a seat. I'll be back.

77
00:08:09,055 --> 00:08:11,071
2 x 6=12

78
00:08:11,595 --> 00:08:14,886
2 x 7 =14

79
00:08:37,020 --> 00:08:38,145
Headmaster!

80
00:08:38,225 --> 00:08:41,098
Hiralal, what's the matter?
-There's a woman to meet you.

81
00:08:41,466 --> 00:08:43,035
Yes, I spoke to the collector.

82
00:08:43,241 --> 00:08:43,996
Is she here?

83
00:08:44,041 --> 00:08:45,837
Yes.
-Hurry up, give me the towel.

84
00:08:46,372 --> 00:08:47,126
Here.

85
00:08:55,075 --> 00:08:57,411
Madam, he's the headmaster.

86
00:08:57,592 --> 00:08:59,593
Mr. Ramnarayan Jha.
-Greetings.

87
00:08:59,643 --> 00:09:02,453
Greetings, my name is Neha Malini.

88
00:09:03,125 --> 00:09:04,244
Neha Malini?

89
00:09:05,294 --> 00:09:08,496
I've heard about Hema Malini.
You are Neha Malini.

90
00:09:08,674 --> 00:09:10,283
Wonderful. Great. Great.

91
00:09:10,304 --> 00:09:12,537
Have a seat. (Chuckles)

92
00:09:13,755 --> 00:09:15,918
So, you've come from Delhi.
-Yes.

93
00:09:16,098 --> 00:09:18,545
I was in US two months ago,
then I came to Delhi...

94
00:09:18,898 --> 00:09:20,889
...then here.
-US?

95
00:09:21,591 --> 00:09:23,301
America.
-America?

96
00:09:23,804 --> 00:09:26,970
Oh, the same America,
where it is night and here it is day?

97
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,945
Hiralal, get two teas.

98
00:09:29,145 --> 00:09:30,333
I've ordered for it.

99
00:09:30,387 --> 00:09:31,567
Special? Okay.
-Yes.

100
00:09:34,489 --> 00:09:37,957
What is this? School map?
-Yes.

101
00:09:38,403 --> 00:09:40,978
Wonderful. It is nice.

102
00:09:42,043 --> 00:09:43,605
It is very big too.

103
00:09:44,192 --> 00:09:46,516
Like King Akbar built Taj Mahal...

104
00:09:46,731 --> 00:09:48,504
...you've come to build a school.

105
00:09:48,919 --> 00:09:52,068
Taj Mahal was not built by Akbar,
but by Shah Jahan.

106
00:09:52,333 --> 00:09:54,725
(Laughs)

107
00:09:55,794 --> 00:09:57,755
Yes, but King Akbar thought about it.

108
00:09:57,887 --> 00:09:59,770
What say?
King Akbar thought about it, right?

109
00:09:59,801 --> 00:10:00,964
Yes...
-Absolutely.

110
00:10:01,622 --> 00:10:04,917
What are you doing here?
Go and teach the children.

111
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:07,097
(Clears throat)

112
00:10:08,762 --> 00:10:10,331
King Akbar thought about it.

113
00:10:10,623 --> 00:10:12,067
Tea...

114
00:10:14,261 --> 00:10:15,417
Here...

115
00:10:16,082 --> 00:10:17,420
Don't you study?
-No.

116
00:10:17,446 --> 00:10:19,555
I make tea for the teachers.

117
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:22,246
Yes. He makes nice tea.

118
00:10:22,483 --> 00:10:25,266
You have it... Here, have tea.

119
00:10:26,426 --> 00:10:30,012
Hey! Hey! Go away!

120
00:10:32,072 --> 00:10:33,267
(Chuckles)

121
00:10:35,083 --> 00:10:38,737
Master, after toiling very hard
and taking help from many people...

122
00:10:38,758 --> 00:10:40,448
...I have arranged for this fund.
-Okay.

123
00:10:41,025 --> 00:10:43,797
You have to make a trust
of local people here.

124
00:10:43,992 --> 00:10:46,602
The school building
will be built in their supervision.

125
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:48,732
Yes, I had spoken the collector.

126
00:10:48,971 --> 00:10:51,286
He said the trust must
consist of five members.

127
00:10:51,741 --> 00:10:55,447
I've spoken to the village chief,
there's an old minister of our village...

128
00:10:55,717 --> 00:10:58,326
...Mr. Kailash... he's very educated.

129
00:10:58,814 --> 00:11:00,483
Moreover, I am present here.

130
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:02,402
And two masters...

131
00:11:02,806 --> 00:11:06,177
Okay, if you feel,
call the others tomorrow.

132
00:11:06,513 --> 00:11:07,360
I'll come tomorrow.

133
00:11:07,672 --> 00:11:09,349
Okay, as you wish.
-Okay.

134
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:13,085
I shall leave.
-Please, come.

135
00:11:13,771 --> 00:11:14,549
Ganga!

136
00:11:15,816 --> 00:11:19,640
What is going on there?
Move them from here. -Hey, go away!

137
00:11:19,961 --> 00:11:21,528
Hey, get down!

138
00:11:21,809 --> 00:11:25,335
Master, I am getting down.
-Do you think it belongs to you?

139
00:11:25,432 --> 00:11:27,528
Hey, how dare you hit a stone!

140
00:11:27,587 --> 00:11:32,210
I will thrash you to pulp.
I will teach you a lesson.

141
00:11:32,758 --> 00:11:34,812
You scoundrel.

142
00:11:34,892 --> 00:11:37,168
I will debar you from the school.

143
00:11:37,487 --> 00:11:38,986
Scoundrel, escaped.

144
00:11:39,311 --> 00:11:42,236
Ms. Neha, you don't worry.
I'll catch hold of him at home.

145
00:11:42,257 --> 00:11:45,447
He will fall on your feet and apologize.
-No need.

146
00:11:46,494 --> 00:11:50,151
Master, I think some children
don't come to school at all.

147
00:11:50,439 --> 00:11:52,484
I met three children from the school...

148
00:11:52,853 --> 00:11:55,461
...they came till here
showing me the way...

149
00:11:55,655 --> 00:11:56,947
...but didn't come inside the school.

150
00:11:57,172 --> 00:11:59,955
Ms. Neha Malini,
children don't come to study here.

151
00:12:00,130 --> 00:12:01,582
They come here to play.

152
00:12:01,710 --> 00:12:04,675
You tell me their names,
I'll get them from their homes.

153
00:12:06,055 --> 00:12:09,542
They said their names were
Hari, Gorak, and Avdesh.

154
00:12:10,348 --> 00:12:11,942
Hari, Gorak, and Avdesh?

155
00:12:13,732 --> 00:12:15,580
Where did you find those three guys?

156
00:12:15,808 --> 00:12:17,257
Why?
-Are you alright?

157
00:12:17,278 --> 00:12:18,020
Yes.

158
00:12:18,041 --> 00:12:21,145
Hope those guys didn't harm you.
-No.

159
00:12:22,084 --> 00:12:24,132
Those three guys are criminals.

160
00:12:24,722 --> 00:12:26,269
What are you saying, Master?
-I'm telling the truth.

161
00:12:26,366 --> 00:12:28,083
They were children aged 12-14 years.

162
00:12:28,163 --> 00:12:31,327
Ms. Neha, they've created chaos
in the entire area.

163
00:12:31,407 --> 00:12:34,042
They've murdered four people.
-Murder?

164
00:12:34,122 --> 00:12:36,227
Yes...
-Ms. Neha, forget it.

165
00:12:36,561 --> 00:12:38,030
We'll concentrate on the school.

166
00:12:52,069 --> 00:13:03,043
(Phone ringing)

167
00:13:04,136 --> 00:13:06,036
Dad?
(Dad)-How are you, my dear?

168
00:13:06,325 --> 00:13:08,682
Have you reached the village? 
-Yes, I've arrived.

169
00:13:08,762 --> 00:13:10,949
What is the name of the village? 
-Birva.

170
00:13:11,736 --> 00:13:14,885
I know you are very excited
as this was your dream.

171
00:13:16,416 --> 00:13:22,885
Dad, I want to celebrate my birthday
with you and mom this year.

172
00:13:23,776 --> 00:13:25,763
Dear, you know, it is not possible.

173
00:13:27,110 --> 00:13:32,709
I am sorry, dear. You didn't get our
love together, but got it separately.

174
00:13:33,008 --> 00:13:36,319
But fulfill your dream for
which you went to that village.

175
00:13:36,482 --> 00:13:39,334
You are happy, I am happy.
Take care.

176
00:13:39,650 --> 00:13:40,572
I am happy, dad.

177
00:13:41,449 --> 00:13:42,226
I love you.

178
00:13:59,383 --> 00:14:01,788
(Neha) DM sir, this school is my dream.

179
00:14:02,140 --> 00:14:05,220
And I need your help.
-You are doing a great job.

180
00:14:06,958 --> 00:14:09,179
I met three children on the way.
-Okay.

181
00:14:10,323 --> 00:14:13,254
They must be aged 12-13 years.
They were innocent.

182
00:14:15,465 --> 00:14:17,795
Then I learnt that they were criminals.

183
00:14:18,910 --> 00:14:21,722
Our police is trying very hard
to nab those three children.

184
00:14:22,184 --> 00:14:22,931
You don't worry.

185
00:14:26,236 --> 00:14:29,182
Sir, I am not worried about myself.

186
00:14:29,675 --> 00:14:31,128
I am worried for those children.

187
00:14:34,542 --> 00:14:38,642
I was a software engineer in America.
I left everything and have come here.

188
00:14:40,258 --> 00:14:41,899
I will finish my work and leave.

189
00:14:50,002 --> 00:14:55,318
(Indistinct chatter)

190
00:15:09,966 --> 00:15:12,386
Greetings, madam. Please, come.

191
00:15:12,882 --> 00:15:15,585
Look there. They've killed someone.
Please, come.

192
00:15:18,342 --> 00:15:20,515
Please, come.
-Who did they kill?

193
00:15:20,536 --> 00:15:21,403
Please come, madam.

194
00:15:23,343 --> 00:15:27,169
Take him out. Come on.

195
00:15:31,493 --> 00:15:32,252
Please, come.

196
00:15:44,407 --> 00:15:46,916
If you get any news about
those three guys, let us know.

197
00:15:48,455 --> 00:15:52,026
Tell their parents to come
and meet me in the police station.

198
00:15:53,625 --> 00:15:56,311
Once if I get hold of them.

199
00:15:58,191 --> 00:15:58,795
Listen...

200
00:16:02,427 --> 00:16:04,799
Who is this madam?
-She's here to build a school.

201
00:16:06,056 --> 00:16:06,815
Really?

202
00:16:08,002 --> 00:16:10,541
Pick up the dead body.
Pick up the dead body!

203
00:16:11,475 --> 00:16:14,178
Careful...
-Come on, pick it up.

204
00:16:14,258 --> 00:16:16,722
Move aside... Move aside.

205
00:16:17,745 --> 00:16:19,813
Can't you hear me?
-Brother, move.

206
00:16:21,623 --> 00:16:24,205
Who killed them?
-Those three guys killed him.

207
00:16:24,285 --> 00:16:27,331
They met you yesterday.
He was constable Mahadev.

208
00:16:28,084 --> 00:16:31,388
They killed him too. Let's go, headmaster
must be waiting for you. Come on.

209
00:16:32,447 --> 00:16:35,048
Ms. Neha, come.
-Greetings, Ms. Neha.

210
00:16:35,614 --> 00:16:38,597
Those three guys killed the constable.
-I heard the news.

211
00:16:38,818 --> 00:16:40,441
I am waiting for you since morning.

212
00:16:40,747 --> 00:16:42,865
I have summoned
the village chief and Mr. Kailash.

213
00:16:43,572 --> 00:16:44,451
Please, come.
-Let's go.

214
00:16:44,634 --> 00:16:45,279
Please, come.

215
00:16:45,877 --> 00:16:46,686
Mr. Kailash.

216
00:16:46,999 --> 00:16:48,164
Greetings.
-He is educated.

217
00:16:48,732 --> 00:16:50,353
I told you about him, didn't I?
-Yes.

218
00:16:50,866 --> 00:16:51,907
He is the chief.

219
00:16:52,120 --> 00:16:52,881
Greetings.
-Greetings.

220
00:16:52,969 --> 00:16:54,586
I help as much as possible.

221
00:16:55,282 --> 00:16:57,210
But this village is in darkness.

222
00:16:57,676 --> 00:16:59,341
There's darkness in this village.

223
00:16:59,989 --> 00:17:01,893
You build the school...

224
00:17:02,220 --> 00:17:04,686
...then children will get educated.

225
00:17:04,736 --> 00:17:07,223
We are ready to support you.
-Yes.

226
00:17:07,336 --> 00:17:11,851
Ms. Neha,
the trustees are in front of you.

227
00:17:11,909 --> 00:17:13,773
(Chuckles)

228
00:17:14,975 --> 00:17:16,797
This file contains all the details.

229
00:17:17,312 --> 00:17:19,247
You read it and sign it.

230
00:17:19,712 --> 00:17:21,955
Since when those three are doing crime?
-Who?

231
00:17:22,539 --> 00:17:24,740
The one who murdered
the constable today.

232
00:17:26,239 --> 00:17:27,372
From four to five months.

233
00:17:27,679 --> 00:17:29,612
You tell me,
where do we have to sign?

234
00:17:30,338 --> 00:17:33,150
Master, I am talking
about those three guys.

235
00:17:37,531 --> 00:17:39,224
I wanted to ask you something.

236
00:17:40,430 --> 00:17:42,948
What is the estimate of this project?

237
00:17:43,251 --> 00:17:44,588
Two crores.

238
00:17:45,387 --> 00:17:46,388
Two crores?

239
00:17:49,613 --> 00:17:50,300
Two...

240
00:17:52,142 --> 00:17:54,466
I am going to Patna
to meet the minister.

241
00:17:54,557 --> 00:17:56,653
Until then you prepare the tender.

242
00:17:56,674 --> 00:17:58,743
We've elected the contractor.

243
00:17:59,475 --> 00:18:04,124
Paras... he is very honest,
respectable, and intelligent contractor.

244
00:18:06,499 --> 00:18:08,830
You are Hariya's mother, right?

245
00:18:08,906 --> 00:18:10,489
What was his enmity with the constable?

246
00:18:10,531 --> 00:18:13,451
No sir, I don't know anything.
-You don't know.

247
00:18:14,361 --> 00:18:16,739
Your child commits a murder
and you don't know anything.

248
00:18:16,955 --> 00:18:18,624
You are Gorak's father, right?
-Yes.

249
00:18:19,609 --> 00:18:20,984
What was his enmity with him?

250
00:18:22,165 --> 00:18:24,776
No one will speak up.
You scoundrels.

251
00:18:26,015 --> 00:18:26,704
You?

252
00:18:28,589 --> 00:18:30,320
Everyone has joined hands in it.

253
00:18:31,812 --> 00:18:34,202
You have begot a goon in the village?
Will you scare us?

254
00:18:44,468 --> 00:18:45,439
Good night, madam.

255
00:18:46,561 --> 00:18:49,785
Good evening.
I am Neha Malini from NGO.

256
00:18:49,865 --> 00:18:51,959
I am Bansi.
I take care of the police station.

257
00:18:52,748 --> 00:18:54,556
