258
00:18:54,636 --> 00:18:55,447
Oh.

259
00:18:57,001 --> 00:18:57,681
Please come.

260
00:19:00,046 --> 00:19:01,374
(Clears throat)

261
00:19:01,454 --> 00:19:02,276
Sir, is the tea ready?

262
00:19:02,297 --> 00:19:03,916
Salute madam.
-Greetings, madam.

263
00:19:07,747 --> 00:19:08,107
Get tea for her.

264
00:19:08,128 --> 00:19:09,632
I'll get it right away.
-Give it to her.

265
00:19:09,716 --> 00:19:11,673
Sir, I've washed it.
-Then go and dry it.

266
00:19:11,694 --> 00:19:12,286
Yes.

267
00:19:15,708 --> 00:19:16,992
Get it... Keep it.
-Here, madam.

268
00:19:17,114 --> 00:19:18,507
Madam, have it.

269
00:19:19,046 --> 00:19:23,289
I heard you met those
three guys on the way.

270
00:19:23,588 --> 00:19:25,750
Yes, they dropped me till the school.

271
00:19:25,878 --> 00:19:28,392
People who are sitting outside
are their parents.

272
00:19:29,224 --> 00:19:30,808
Mother, father of criminals.

273
00:19:31,525 --> 00:19:32,640
Nonsense people.

274
00:19:33,117 --> 00:19:35,064
Hey, tell madam how many
murderers they've committed.

275
00:19:35,085 --> 00:19:36,535
Four...
-Four.

276
00:19:37,419 --> 00:19:38,724
Today was the fifth.

277
00:19:39,397 --> 00:19:42,463
He was our constable. They
killed him by drowning him in a well.

278
00:19:43,078 --> 00:19:44,367
You were there.

279
00:19:45,690 --> 00:19:47,127
This area is such.

280
00:19:47,947 --> 00:19:50,865
It is not life...
everyone is living in fear.

281
00:19:52,555 --> 00:19:56,609
Madam, what do you do?
-I opened a NGO.

282
00:19:57,184 --> 00:19:59,242
And this... family?

283
00:20:01,221 --> 00:20:03,935
Father is a scientist
and my mother is a professor.

284
00:20:04,486 --> 00:20:10,608
And I... Madam, I am...
Inspector Balkishan.

285
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:15,515
But sir, for how long will these
three guys keep murdering people?

286
00:20:15,689 --> 00:20:17,773
You have to arrest them.

287
00:20:18,233 --> 00:20:22,707
I have to do... but how? What?

288
00:20:23,112 --> 00:20:24,193
You tell me...

289
00:20:24,337 --> 00:20:27,082
...the entire police department
will help you building the school...

290
00:20:27,182 --> 00:20:28,838
Department, will you help her or not?

291
00:20:28,860 --> 00:20:32,243
Sir, we'll help her...
-Madam, we'll help you whenever you want.

292
00:20:33,787 --> 00:20:35,884
