-Okay, madam.

293
00:20:37,638 --> 00:20:39,756
Hey, salute madam.
-Greetings, madam.

294
00:20:39,777 --> 00:20:41,108
Please come...

295
00:20:42,663 --> 00:20:45,217
You go peacefully and return.

296
00:20:45,915 --> 00:20:48,956
Look, I'm investigating them.
Be seated, I'll be back.

297
00:20:50,109 --> 00:20:53,704
We'll surely nab those guys.

298
00:20:54,289 --> 00:20:57,863
You go peacefully and until you return,
I'll finish my enquiry.

299
00:20:58,173 --> 00:21:00,309
Okay... I shall leave.
-Please, sit.

300
00:21:02,194 --> 00:21:04,225
(Bird chirping)

301
00:21:05,123 --> 00:21:05,850
(Door closed sound)

302
