336
00:23:32,025 --> 00:23:34,098
(Gunshot)
-(Groans)

337
00:24:04,654 --> 00:24:11,491
Greetings. Wow...
all the trustees are present here.

338
00:24:16,550 --> 00:24:19,004
I heard that those
three guys killed Paras.

339
00:24:22,671 --> 00:24:26,731
Those three guys are very mischievous,
dangerous, and crazy guys.

340
00:24:28,249 --> 00:24:32,438
