"Beloved."

445
00:33:33,626 --> 00:33:42,234
"Beloved went ahead me.
What do I do?"

446
00:33:42,314 --> 00:33:46,519
"Beloved went ahead me.
What do I do?"

447
00:33:46,575 --> 00:33:50,383
"Beloved is very mischievous.
What do I do?"

448
00:33:50,424 --> 00:33:58,748
"Beloved is very mischievous.
What do I do? What do I do?"

449
00:33:58,828 --> 00:34:05,978
"When I was 15 years old,
they bid farewell to me."

