"Beloved."

453
00:34:24,970 --> 00:34:29,235
"Beloved calls out for his mother.
What do I do?"

454
00:34:29,315 --> 00:34:33,344
"Beloved calls out for his mother.
What do I do?"

455
00:34:33,513 --> 00:34:37,708
"Beloved calls out for his mother.
What do I do?" -Let's go.

456
00:34:37,788 --> 00:34:41,451
"Beloved is very mischievous.
What do I do?" -Come on, hurry up.

457
00:34:41,937 --> 00:34:49,045
"Beloved is very mischievous.
What do I do?" -Hey, come on. Come on!

458
00:35:01,032 --> 00:35:04,140
"What do I do?"
-Come on!

459
00:35:11,990 --> 00:35:12,707
Take this.

460
00:35:16,134 --> 00:35:19,579
It is more than Rs. 10,000.
Give back Poonam.

461
00:35:21,930 --> 00:35:22,968
(Spitting)

462
00:35:23,669 --> 00:35:24,785
You delayed.

463
00:35:26,103 --> 00:35:28,225
