We've already sold her.

465
00:35:33,869 --> 00:35:36,435
You can't do anything now.
-How could you sell her!

466
00:35:37,080 --> 00:35:40,552
How could you sell her!
How dare you!

467
00:35:40,599 --> 00:35:43,275
How dare you!
-You argue with me!

468
00:35:43,845 --> 00:35:45,231
(Wailing)

469
00:35:45,364 --> 00:35:47,287
Your father has taken loan from us.

470
00:35:49,153 --> 00:35:52,559
Tell him to repay
the loan at the earliest.

471
00:35:53,626 --> 00:35:55,440
If not, we'll sell you too.

472
00:36:00,891 --> 00:36:01,704
(Spitting)

473
00:36:16,774 --> 00:36:19,520
Rama Shankar is strange man.

474
00:36:19,990 --> 00:36:22,228
He has to pay loan and...

475
00:36:22,647 --> 00:36:25,773
