with our son.

476
00:36:27,164 --> 00:36:30,453
This means, can he abduct Poonam?

477
00:36:30,810 --> 00:36:32,802
Will he sell her anywhere?

478
00:36:33,340 --> 00:36:34,889
Even you have to repay him loan.

479
00:36:35,883 --> 00:36:39,599
