483
00:36:55,381 --> 00:36:59,799
We'll repay the loan.
We'll repay the loan.

484
00:37:00,597 --> 00:37:09,544
We'll repay the loan...
We'll repay the loan...

485
00:37:24,367 --> 00:37:25,162
Eat food.

486
00:37:27,476 --> 00:37:28,987
(Horse neighing)

487
00:37:29,067 --> 00:37:31,165
Hey, get it down... careful.

488
00:37:32,083 --> 00:37:37,919
(Indistinct chatter)

489
00:37:38,865 --> 00:37:41,260
(Cycle bell ringing)

490
00:38:04,445 --> 00:38:05,829
Raghuveer has sent me to you.

491
00:38:07,080 --> 00:38:08,653
He has asked me to get the money.

492
00:38:09,808 --> 00:38:11,443
The lentil crops are going
to be harvested.

493
00:38:12,421 --> 00:38:13,718
Give us one more month's time.

494
00:38:15,219 --> 00:38:17,262
Your boy keeps roaming here and there.

495
00:38:18,627 --> 00:38:19,677
Shall I talk about him?

496
00:38:20,231 --> 00:38:22,757
He will get a job.
He'll get Rs. 10,000.

497
00:38:23,028 --> 00:38:24,717
He'll get Rs. 500 monthly as tips.

498
00:38:25,458 --> 00:38:28,184
Raghuveer sold his fiancée.

499
00:38:29,259 --> 00:38:31,459
Now he is eyeing on him.

500
00:38:32,985 --> 00:38:34,845
Then I'll take your cattle.

501
00:38:35,677 --> 00:38:39,496
If you take cattle,
how will we live?

502
00:38:44,583 --> 00:38:48,853
Hey... Do anything you feel like.
You've made our life miserable.

503
00:38:51,805 --> 00:38:53,308
The capital amount is Rs. 5000.

504
00:38:53,785 --> 00:38:57,110
Interest money is Rs. 4000.
You have to pay Rs. 9000.

505
00:38:57,252 --> 00:39:00,261
Tie the cattle...
I'll come with you tomorrow.

506
00:39:03,556 --> 00:39:04,963
You'll get Rs. 10,000.

507
00:39:06,178 --> 00:39:08,282
Mr. Raghuveer will wave off
your interest money.

508
00:39:10,367 --> 00:39:11,034
Understood?

509
00:39:11,811 --> 00:39:15,355
He'll give Rs. 5000 to your father.
(Chuckles)

510
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:30,814
I'm going with Dhooman today.

511
00:39:35,696 --> 00:39:36,715
Where are you going?

512
00:39:38,597 --> 00:39:42,026
I don't know. I have to
go if I have to save the cattle.

513
00:39:43,060 --> 00:39:45,261
My parents will die
if the cattle are not here.

514
00:39:45,921 --> 00:39:47,733
We both will die without you.

515
00:39:49,367 --> 00:39:51,157
We will not let you go.

516
00:39:53,016 --> 00:39:55,975
Let me go... who knows,
I may find Poonam there.

517
00:39:56,026 --> 00:39:57,696
I may even get a chance to free her.

518
00:39:58,069 --> 00:39:59,403
We'll find Poonam for you.

519
00:39:59,637 --> 00:40:01,891
Let's go, we'll talk to Dhooman.

520
00:40:17,121 --> 00:40:18,626
(Goat bleats)

521
00:40:22,249 --> 00:40:23,679
(Goat bleats)

522
00:40:28,732 --> 00:40:31,234
Come, I've been waiting for you.

523
00:40:32,499 --> 00:40:36,391
Hey Dhooman, go away...
Avdesh will not go with you.

524
00:40:38,259 --> 00:40:40,376
You are talking too much?

525
00:40:44,423 --> 00:40:47,112
You!
-Move... why did you hit him?

526
00:40:47,341 --> 00:40:50,570
Hey, hit him...
-I am telling you.

527
00:40:50,650 --> 00:40:56,611
How dare you!
-Why are you hitting me?

528
00:40:56,989 --> 00:40:59,678
Wait...
-I'll teach you a lesson.

529
00:40:59,758 --> 00:41:01,135
Get out!
-Hit him.

530
00:41:01,156 --> 00:41:03,185
Get going!
-He'll teach you a lesson.

531
00:41:03,368 --> 00:41:05,057
I'll not spare you.

532
00:41:14,850 --> 00:41:19,191
He got saved or we would've
thrashed him to pulp. (Laughs)

533
00:41:19,266 --> 00:41:23,962
Avdesh, Raghuveer and his men
are hitting your dad in the farm.

534
00:41:36,385 --> 00:41:39,694
(Indistinct chatter)

535
00:41:58,800 --> 00:42:01,503
Father!
-Uncle? Uncle?

536
00:42:01,583 --> 00:42:03,975
Father...
-We'll not spare you, scoundrels!

537
00:42:04,153 --> 00:42:05,894
Uncle!
-He killed my father.

538
00:42:05,974 --> 00:42:09,124
Father! Father!

539
00:42:09,281 --> 00:42:11,894
Scoundrels killed my father.

540
00:42:25,258 --> 00:42:26,405
Contractor, how much is it?

541
00:42:27,326 --> 00:42:28,463
It is Rs. 25,000.

542
00:42:29,975 --> 00:42:31,845
We killed Manohar.

543
00:42:34,012 --> 00:42:35,891
I've committed 2-3 murders for you.

544
00:42:36,988 --> 00:42:39,042
I've abducted many children.

545
00:42:39,122 --> 00:42:42,366
But I never told
your name to the police.

546
00:42:43,758 --> 00:42:47,411
Contractor, it would've been nice
if you would give me more Rs. 25,000.

547
00:43:02,338 --> 00:43:04,023
Contractor, don't feel bad...

548
00:43:04,560 --> 00:43:07,563
...I am in need of money.
-Why will I feel bad?

549
00:43:07,861 --> 00:43:08,933
Goodbye.

550
00:43:14,454 --> 00:43:18,334
Boss, Raghuveer is becoming greedy.

551
00:43:19,959 --> 00:43:21,398
Let he be greedy...

552
00:43:24,618 --> 00:43:27,034
...he has been calculating things
these days.

553
00:43:32,305 --> 00:43:35,128
Get those three guys to me.

554
00:43:35,842 --> 00:43:38,554
You don't worry.
Boss is calling you. Come on.

555
00:43:40,873 --> 00:43:44,662
(Barks)

556
00:43:53,780 --> 00:43:55,921
Come on... don't get scared.
Come on.

557
00:44:02,952 --> 00:44:03,871
(Sighs)

558
00:44:06,415 --> 00:44:08,802
Bhola...
-Yes, boss?

559
00:44:09,715 --> 00:44:11,159
Where will we find Raghuveer?

560
00:44:11,673 --> 00:44:13,755
He is constructing his shop.

561
00:44:13,776 --> 00:44:16,375
He has got Rs. 50,000.
So, he is doing it.

562
00:44:20,998 --> 00:44:25,837
Come...
-Come, sit. Sit.

563
00:44:30,208 --> 00:44:31,300
(Sighs)

564
00:44:33,873 --> 00:44:35,765
Come...
-Yes.

565
00:44:40,508 --> 00:44:41,434
Sit here.

566
00:44:43,937 --> 00:44:44,656
Sit.

567
00:44:54,441 --> 00:44:55,223
(Sighs)

568
00:45:05,348 --> 00:45:06,715
Have you killed an ant?

569
00:45:09,974 --> 00:45:11,083
You would've killed a rat too?

570
00:45:12,531 --> 00:45:13,812
You would've killed a snake too.

571
00:45:14,910 --> 00:45:17,779
Did you kill it or not? Then?
-Yes, we've killed it.

572
00:45:18,613 --> 00:45:20,491
It is not difficult to kill
a human being.

573
00:45:23,318 --> 00:45:29,183
Come here...
-Go... Boss is calling you. Go to him.

574
00:45:31,997 --> 00:45:32,938
Come, come.

575
00:45:35,132 --> 00:45:35,821
Come, sit here.

576
00:45:38,243 --> 00:45:43,606
Killing a human is not a big deal.
You just need to have guts.

577
00:45:45,281 --> 00:45:46,723
Bhola.
-Yes, boss?

578
00:45:47,736 --> 00:45:49,149
Give the things to them.

579
00:46:02,619 --> 00:46:03,276
Here.

580
00:46:05,316 --> 00:46:08,774
You also take...
-Practice in the jungle.

581
00:46:11,200 --> 00:46:14,633
You'll get Raghuveer in his shop.

582
00:46:17,120 --> 00:46:18,891
If you are in need of money...

583
00:46:19,442 --> 00:46:21,556
...then don't ask anyone.

584
00:46:22,634 --> 00:46:23,747
Come to me.

585
00:46:25,258 --> 00:46:26,875
Your father died...

586
00:46:28,574 --> 00:46:31,196
...hereafter, I am your father.

587
00:46:34,095 --> 00:46:36,438
We'll get your bride back.

588
00:46:37,997 --> 00:46:38,875
Understood?

589
00:46:40,593 --> 00:46:41,139
Go.

590
00:46:44,884 --> 00:46:46,095
(Laughs)

591
00:46:46,379 --> 00:46:47,035
Let's go.

592
00:46:51,984 --> 00:47:01,697
(Singing)

593
00:47:17,891 --> 00:47:19,058
(Gunshot)

594
00:47:45,522 --> 00:47:46,802
(Barks)

595
00:47:58,416 --> 00:48:00,284
(Barks)

596
00:48:03,335 --> 00:48:06,904
Where's your son?
Have you hidden him inside?

597
00:48:07,443 --> 00:48:10,686
He's not at home.
-He murdered.

598
00:48:11,121 --> 00:48:12,520
Do you know that?

599
00:48:14,143 --> 00:48:16,229
How about your husband?

600
00:48:17,229 --> 00:48:19,675
How about your son?

601
00:48:21,222 --> 00:48:24,560
You are alone.
What all will you endure?

602
00:48:27,215 --> 00:48:28,741
If you need me...

603
00:48:29,545 --> 00:48:33,457
...meet me... at my quarters.

604
00:48:37,972 --> 00:48:44,925
"I spoke to my darling at night."

605
00:48:47,587 --> 00:48:49,451
(Bike engine starts)

606
00:48:50,768 --> 00:48:55,245
(Bike passing sound)

607
00:49:03,851 --> 00:49:11,961
(Muslim prayer)

608
00:49:38,959 --> 00:49:40,986
What all I am going through
because of you...

609
00:49:56,092 --> 00:50:02,549
Why? Why did you kill him?

610
00:50:03,707 --> 00:50:05,136
Tell me! Tell me!

611
00:50:06,837 --> 00:50:09,311
I will thrash you. Tell me!

612
00:50:09,735 --> 00:50:13,342
Will you tell me or not?
Why did you kill him? -Mother? Mother?

613
00:50:13,458 --> 00:50:17,310
You've made my life miserable.
Why did you...?

614
00:50:17,549 --> 00:50:20,116
He killed my father...
so I killed him.

615
00:50:22,757 --> 00:50:27,036
I am going... I am leaving the house.
I'll never return.

616
00:50:32,796 --> 00:50:34,404
Avdesh! Avdesh!

617
00:50:37,025 --> 00:50:38,011
Avdesh!

618
00:51:13,778 --> 00:51:14,804
Where are they three?

619
00:51:15,785 --> 00:51:16,909
They are going to Patna.

620
00:51:17,965 --> 00:51:18,973
To look for Poonam.

621
00:51:25,128 --> 00:51:27,924
There's somebody named
Ranjan in Ameethapur.

622
00:51:29,633 --> 00:51:30,708
Mahesh told me.

623
00:51:37,586 --> 00:51:39,349
Lakhan is a big criminal.

624
00:51:40,294 --> 00:51:42,703
He made three innocent children
as criminal.

625
00:51:43,512 --> 00:51:45,135
He is using them.

626
00:51:46,285 --> 00:51:49,364
You gave him the contract.

627
00:51:49,545 --> 00:51:52,884
Neha dear,
you are doing a good deed.

628
00:51:53,354 --> 00:51:55,380
We want that good deed
to get completed.

629
00:51:55,997 --> 00:51:58,219
What do we have to do
with Lakhan's past?

630
00:51:59,074 --> 00:52:01,971
He is working... we just need
the work to be done. That's it.

631
00:52:02,731 --> 00:52:04,998
Mr. Kailash,
touch your heart and tell me...

632
00:52:05,425 --> 00:52:08,105
...is it okay if a hooligan
does this good deed?

633
00:52:08,230 --> 00:52:08,952
Ms. Neha...

634
00:52:11,403 --> 00:52:13,943
...talk softly, somebody may hear you.

635
00:52:14,080 --> 00:52:16,668
Hiralal says that
Lakhan is a bad man.

636
00:52:17,168 --> 00:52:19,628
We shouldn't take risk
by talking against him.

637
00:52:20,126 --> 00:52:22,364
We'll all do the work...
what's wrong in it?

638
00:52:23,172 --> 00:52:25,658
A criminal can't build
a school building.

639
00:52:25,688 --> 00:52:27,756
Criminal?
He's not a criminal, but a shrew.

640
00:52:28,081 --> 00:52:29,924
He hasn't started working on
my house yet.

641
00:52:31,071 --> 00:52:31,995
Your house?

642
00:52:38,264 --> 00:52:39,276
I'm going to Patna.

643
00:52:39,467 --> 00:52:41,807
Tell Lakhan to stay away from this job.

644
00:52:42,037 --> 00:52:44,059
I'll return and talk to you.
-No.

645
00:52:44,080 --> 00:52:45,805
Goodbye...
-Listen...

646
00:52:47,949 --> 00:52:48,763
(Sighs)

647
00:52:49,885 --> 00:52:52,166
Hit him!
-It slipped out of my mouth.

648
00:52:52,246 --> 00:52:54,653
You should've kept your mouth shut!
How could you...

649
00:52:54,674 --> 00:52:56,228
Shut up!
-He ruined our plans.

650
00:52:56,249 --> 00:52:56,782
Oh no.

651
00:53:40,608 --> 00:53:43,463
Open... open the window.

652
00:53:53,423 --> 00:53:55,543
Cool breeze.
-It is cool breeze.

653
00:53:55,888 --> 00:53:57,195
Increase the speed.

654
00:53:57,477 --> 00:53:59,131
Yes, increase the speed.

655
00:54:02,719 --> 00:54:04,680
Water...

656
00:54:07,611 --> 00:54:09,715
Play a song...
-Come on, play it.

657
00:54:25,484 --> 00:54:33,119
"Which place is this?
It is a four feet wall."

658
00:54:33,199 --> 00:54:40,065
"O sir, we got sold cheaper
than the cattle."

659
00:54:43,766 --> 00:54:50,983
"Which place is this?
It is a four feet wall."

660
00:54:51,538 --> 00:54:58,286
"O sir, we got sold cheaper
than the cattle."

661
00:54:58,454 --> 00:55:05,215
"O sir, our tears are
flowing non-stop."

662
00:55:06,627 --> 00:55:09,328
Children aged 12-13 years
have become criminals.

663
00:55:10,136 --> 00:55:11,448
They are committing murders.

664
00:55:13,456 --> 00:55:15,776
Child trafficking is also
a big problem in that village.

665
00:55:16,708 --> 00:55:19,955
Boys are sold and bought for
Rs. 5000 to Rs. 10,000.

666
00:55:25,876 --> 00:55:30,941
There's someone named Ranjan in
Ameethapur here... he's behind everything.

667
00:55:32,140 --> 00:55:36,153
Find him out.
-Ameethapur? That's a red-light area.

668
00:55:40,794 --> 00:55:43,727
We can put NGO pressure
on Ameethapur police station...

669
00:55:43,831 --> 00:55:44,935
...we can take their help.

670
00:56:12,579 --> 00:56:14,651
Hey, does Ranjan stay here?

671
00:56:15,768 --> 00:56:17,819
Yes, upstairs. Go.
-Okay.

672
00:56:32,403 --> 00:56:34,997
Here... see if it contains
Poonam's photo in it.

673
00:57:08,793 --> 00:57:11,480
Is she Poonam?
You'll get her tomorrow morning.

674
00:57:13,544 --> 00:57:15,697
You've come from far.
You must be tired. So, take rest.

675
00:57:16,606 --> 00:57:18,249
I will send food for you all.

676
00:57:19,253 --> 00:57:21,289
I respect Mr. Lakhan very much.

677
00:57:22,117 --> 00:57:25,419
You are fortunate that
you got Poonam so easily.

678
00:57:25,614 --> 00:57:27,751
I'll be back.
You don't go anywhere.

679
00:57:28,600 --> 00:57:29,439
Stay here.

680
00:57:33,889 --> 00:57:35,131
(Door closed sounds)

681
00:57:35,375 --> 00:57:36,832
(Door locked)

682
00:57:40,657 --> 00:57:42,345
(Laughs)

683
00:57:42,667 --> 00:57:46,343
Uncle, I've locked those
three guys in the room.

684
00:57:46,694 --> 00:57:49,181
Take care of them.
-Who are they three?

685
00:57:49,311 --> 00:57:51,379
They are birds.

686
00:57:51,572 --> 00:57:53,518
They came flying to me.

687
00:57:54,559 --> 00:57:55,344
Take care.

688
00:57:55,585 --> 00:57:59,924
(Police siren)

689
00:58:01,486 --> 00:58:03,126
We were looking for an opportunity.

690
00:58:04,221 --> 00:58:06,327
There's something wrong going on
in this mansion.

691
00:58:07,062 --> 00:58:09,368
Ranjan was on
our radar from long time.

692
00:58:10,207 --> 00:58:12,192
Your NGO has given us
this opportunity...

693
00:58:12,559 --> 00:58:14,464
...by putting pressure on
our Department.

694
00:58:16,329 --> 00:58:18,220
Shall we?
-Yes.

695
00:58:19,829 --> 00:58:23,181
"Your silky tresses."

696
00:58:24,221 --> 00:58:27,590
Hey, you didn't find anyone?
-Why are you standing here?

697
00:58:31,004 --> 00:58:34,194
Go away...
-Come on.

698
00:58:34,409 --> 00:58:36,301
Police! Police! Flee!

699
00:58:40,234 --> 00:58:43,193
Do you know Ranjan?
Do you know him?

700
00:58:44,017 --> 00:58:45,882
Where is Ranjan?
-I don't know.

701
00:58:48,206 --> 00:58:50,737
Hey, who is Ranjan? Where is he?
-He's there.

702
00:58:50,758 --> 00:58:51,415
Ranjan!

703
00:58:53,260 --> 00:58:57,085
Who is it? -I am your father!
Scoundrel, open the door!

704
00:58:57,165 --> 00:59:00,804
Open the door! Open it!
-(Door knocking)

705
00:59:03,476 --> 00:59:04,724
Are you Ranjan!

706
00:59:06,354 --> 00:59:08,449
Are you Ranjan!
-No.

707
00:59:09,232 --> 00:59:10,467
Tell me...
-No.

708
00:59:10,488 --> 00:59:11,760
Sir, there are children here.

709
00:59:33,299 --> 00:59:40,495
"You hurt me so much that
my dreams shattered."

710
00:59:40,624 --> 00:59:47,827
"Oh sir, no one should be born as girl."

711
00:59:52,287 --> 00:59:53,287
Where is Poonam?

712
00:59:54,693 --> 00:59:55,673
Speak up!

713
00:59:57,896 --> 00:59:59,638
Who is Poonam amongst you?

714
01:00:02,922 --> 01:00:04,066
From Birwa village.

715
01:00:05,247 --> 01:00:06,090
It is her.

716
01:00:06,544 --> 01:00:13,450
"The house is on the river bank
of Ganges in the east."

717
01:00:13,896 --> 01:00:23,651
"Oh sir, I am three miles away
from the home now."

718
01:00:24,225 --> 01:00:28,927
(Police siren)

719
01:00:33,910 --> 01:00:35,444
You go and look there.
-Okay, sir.

720
01:00:36,342 --> 01:00:37,160
Let's go.

721
01:00:43,963 --> 01:00:46,233
Who is inside? Hey!

722
01:00:49,248 --> 01:00:50,177
Is anyone inside?

723
01:00:55,559 --> 01:00:57,140
Hey, open the door.
-(Door knocking)

724
01:00:59,512 --> 01:01:01,918
Where's Ranjan's house?
-Sir, this is the one.

725
01:01:03,788 --> 01:01:05,649
Constable!
-Yes, sir?

726
01:01:05,800 --> 01:01:07,333
Get something to break the lock.
-Okay.

727
01:01:08,699 --> 01:01:11,488
(Door knocking)

728
01:01:12,335 --> 01:01:14,830
Avdesh, are you alright?

729
01:01:14,910 --> 01:01:16,844
(Door knocking)

730
01:01:16,924 --> 01:01:18,152
Sir, take this.
-Yes.

731
01:01:20,560 --> 01:01:22,128
(Door knocking)

732
01:01:27,911 --> 01:01:30,546
Hey, move back...
-Move back.

733
01:01:30,626 --> 01:01:32,179
Avdesh...
-Move back...

734
01:01:32,200 --> 01:01:34,160
Avdesh, listen to me.

735
01:01:34,220 --> 01:01:35,400
Move back...

736
01:01:35,421 --> 01:01:37,093
Hey.
-Run!

737
01:01:37,153 --> 01:01:39,668
Avdesh!
-Constable, nab him!

738
01:01:39,748 --> 01:01:43,883
Hey, surround them!
-I'm telling you to stop! Stop!

739
01:01:46,315 --> 01:01:48,167
Hari!
-Run!

740
01:01:48,572 --> 01:01:50,221
Stop!

741
01:01:50,680 --> 01:01:52,585
Hey, stop!

742
01:02:01,666 --> 01:02:02,798
They escaped in the dark.

743
01:02:03,653 --> 01:02:04,579
It is hard to find them.

744
01:02:05,869 --> 01:02:06,859
I know them.

745
01:02:11,883 --> 01:02:12,697
Thank you, Ms. Neha.

746
01:02:13,625 --> 01:02:17,385
Because of your information, we've
caught hold of human trafficking gang.

747
01:02:18,264 --> 01:02:21,282
We have sent all the children
to child refuge.

748
01:02:21,809 --> 01:02:24,041
You got your Poonam back.

749
01:02:32,597 --> 01:02:34,702
You please have a seat. Sit.

750
01:02:35,894 --> 01:02:38,572
By the way,
where are those guys from?

751
01:02:39,157 --> 01:02:42,884
There's a village named Birwa near
Betiya, they belong to that place.

752
01:02:43,600 --> 01:02:46,533
Ranjan has revealed everything.
A man named Lakhan...

753
01:02:47,301 --> 01:02:49,533
...he is the chief of child abduction.

754
01:02:57,072 --> 01:03:00,129
Lakhan is a hardcore criminal.
He makes criminals.

755
01:03:01,384 --> 01:03:02,905
He is involved in child trafficking too.

756
01:03:03,548 --> 01:03:05,509
No one is doing anything against him.

757
01:03:06,883 --> 01:03:08,511
Lakhan should be removed from this job...

758
01:03:08,612 --> 01:03:10,297
...and this contract should be
handed over to someone else.

759
01:03:11,539 --> 01:03:16,958
Ms. Neha, do we need Vibhishan
to win over Lanka or not? Tell me.

760
01:03:18,010 --> 01:03:21,533
Lakhan is a bad man.
He'll have work...

761
01:03:21,648 --> 01:03:23,365
...then everything will go on smoothly.

762
01:03:23,782 --> 01:03:27,188
Your school will get
completed on time, right?

763
01:03:27,417 --> 01:03:29,241
Look, you must be mistaken.

764
01:03:29,897 --> 01:03:33,249
I know Lakhan personally.
He's a nice man.

765
01:03:34,401 --> 01:03:35,097
(Chuckles)

766
01:03:35,506 --> 01:03:39,389
I'm seeing love in your eyes
since the first day.

767
01:03:39,898 --> 01:03:42,864
What?
-For the village.

768
01:03:44,546 --> 01:03:46,479
I am seeing love in your eyes...

769
01:03:46,815 --> 01:03:48,221
...for the children of the village.

770
01:03:48,301 --> 01:03:51,196
Shall I suggest you something?
Why don't you join politics?

771
01:03:51,978 --> 01:03:54,679
I give you the guarantee of
getting a ticket.

772
01:03:55,910 --> 01:03:59,991
When a beautiful girl like you will
stand on the stage for a speech...

773
01:04:00,127 --> 01:04:03,276
then we need not toil to get the crowd...
-I am not interested in joining politics.

774
01:04:04,072 --> 01:04:05,781
I will expose Lakhan.

775
01:04:06,680 --> 01:04:09,567
But I think, many more people
will be exposed with Lakhan.

776
01:04:12,368 --> 01:04:16,199
Ms. Neha, you got angry.

777
01:04:18,276 --> 01:04:20,571
You want to remove Lakhan, right?

778
01:04:20,760 --> 01:04:22,530
Yes.
-Okay, I'll remove him.

779
01:04:23,449 --> 01:04:26,256
Give me... where do I have to sign?
Give it to me.

780
01:04:30,894 --> 01:04:34,090
(Crickets creaking)

781
01:04:54,756 --> 01:04:58,365
Hey, get it. Hurry up.
-Yes, I'll get it.

782
01:05:33,322 --> 01:05:36,947
"By cleaning the house and courtyard...

783
01:05:37,027 --> 01:05:40,663
...and after washing the dishes...

784
01:05:40,743 --> 01:05:47,960
...I became like the branch of
the tree, Oh sir."

785
01:05:51,690 --> 01:05:58,987
"By cleaning the house and courtyard
and after washing the dishes...

786
01:05:59,032 --> 01:06:06,270
...I became like the branch of
the tree, Oh sir." -Poonam?

787
01:06:06,350 --> 01:06:13,609
"You took the money
and chopped me off."

788
01:06:14,054 --> 01:06:20,838
"Oh sir, you made a
daughter as an animal."

789
01:06:20,918 --> 01:06:28,243
"Oh sir, you made a daughter
as an animal."

790
01:06:28,323 --> 01:06:35,704
"Oh sir, my tears are flowing non-stop."
-Madam...

791
01:06:43,038 --> 01:06:46,302
What are you watching?
Go and inform her parents.

792
01:06:46,415 --> 01:06:49,185
Go and inform her parents, son.

793
01:06:49,265 --> 01:06:52,604
Your parents will be so happy.

794
01:06:53,024 --> 01:06:56,636
My child is back...

795
01:06:59,778 --> 01:07:01,226
May god bless you.

796
01:07:03,252 --> 01:07:07,198
"It is a four feet wall."

797
01:07:07,278 --> 01:07:14,041
"Oh sir, I got sold cheaper
than the cattle."

798
01:07:17,837 --> 01:07:25,161
"Which place is this?
It is a four feet wall."

799
01:07:25,470 --> 01:07:32,326
"Oh sir, I got sold cheaper
than the cattle."

800
01:07:35,109 --> 01:07:42,084
(Indistinct chatter)

801
01:07:43,270 --> 01:07:47,081
Hey, give it to me...
come on, throw it down.

802
01:07:48,569 --> 01:07:52,250
Hey, careful...
-Give it to me.

803
01:07:52,390 --> 01:07:53,864
Take this... Take this.

804
01:07:53,944 --> 01:07:55,561
Bhola...
-Yes, sir?

805
01:07:55,755 --> 01:07:59,243
I heard, you get such
goggles in the city...

806
01:07:59,810 --> 01:08:02,013
...in which you can see
under the clothes.

807
01:08:02,851 --> 01:08:05,054
Boss, you are right.
Even I heard that.

808
01:08:07,170 --> 01:08:11,000
Madam, please come. Look, the
construction of the school has begun.

809
01:08:12,555 --> 01:08:13,753
Lakhan, what is this?

810
01:08:15,067 --> 01:08:16,377
These are bricks.

811
01:08:17,451 --> 01:08:20,521
I am not talking about bricks.
I'm talking about children.

812
01:08:21,662 --> 01:08:22,706
Yes, they are children.

813
01:08:23,743 --> 01:08:26,241
I think you don't know that
making children work...

814
01:08:26,262 --> 01:08:27,992
...who are under 18 years, is a crime.

815
01:08:28,575 --> 01:08:29,528
Is it?

816
01:08:32,001 --> 01:08:33,602
Give it to me...
-What is this?

817
01:08:33,743 --> 01:08:36,460
Children, stop it. Come down.
-Hey...

818
01:08:36,516 --> 01:08:38,134
Stop it...
-Come down.

819
01:08:38,155 --> 01:08:39,360
Get down.
-Let's go.

820
01:08:39,459 --> 01:08:41,008
Go...
-Go to your house.

821
01:08:41,088 --> 01:08:44,379
You go now. Come after you
have crossed 18 years.

822
01:08:46,962 --> 01:08:49,001
He's doing crime.
-Yes.

823
01:08:49,081 --> 01:08:51,341
Take this.
-What is this?

824
01:08:51,813 --> 01:08:53,105
It is minister's letter.

825
01:08:53,419 --> 01:08:55,555
You've been removed
from this contract.

826
01:08:57,986 --> 01:08:59,248
What?

827
01:08:59,803 --> 01:09:03,327
Your work is done.
Enough, you may leave now.

828
01:09:16,202 --> 01:09:17,841
(Engine starts)

829
01:09:26,454 --> 01:09:29,823
Ms. Neha, what have you done?
You sacked Lakhan.

830
01:09:31,020 --> 01:09:33,234
I didn't sack Lakhan,
but Mr. Baldev did.

831
01:09:33,755 --> 01:09:35,711
Baldev is incarnation of God here.

832
01:09:35,931 --> 01:09:37,511
Lakhan is the owner.

833
01:09:37,648 --> 01:09:39,543
We are just pawns.

834
01:09:39,991 --> 01:09:44,839
Even we'll resign from the trust.
If we are alive, we'll built a house.

835
01:09:45,042 --> 01:09:48,543
Ms. Neha, you look for another
village to build your school.

836
01:09:48,662 --> 01:09:50,431
Go away. Immediately.

837
01:09:51,618 --> 01:09:55,303
You don't worry.
My NGO will handle the trust.

838
01:09:59,076 --> 01:10:00,373
She is very adamant.

839
01:10:00,986 --> 01:10:02,540
Let's go to Mr. Lakhan.
-Come.

840
01:10:02,620 --> 01:10:04,608
Before he avenges us...
-Let's go.

841
01:10:04,629 --> 01:10:06,638
We can't trust him.
He can do anything.

842
01:10:10,330 --> 01:10:11,852
Everyone is here?

843
01:10:11,932 --> 01:10:13,095
Brother Lakhan...

844
01:10:13,116 --> 01:10:15,561
Brother Lakhan, forgive us.
-What's the matter?

845
01:10:15,621 --> 01:10:18,270
Leave my legs.
-No, until you don't forgive us...

846
01:10:18,350 --> 01:10:20,108
...we will not leave your legs.

847
01:10:20,188 --> 01:10:22,465
Okay, I forgive you.

848
01:10:24,081 --> 01:10:26,987
He forgave us.
-My three lions are here.

849
01:10:27,051 --> 01:10:28,902
You get up and go home.

850
01:10:29,479 --> 01:10:32,083
Look, I will build the school.

851
01:10:32,357 --> 01:10:34,290
You just support me.

852
01:10:34,484 --> 01:10:37,769
Goodbye... Go, go.
-Goodbye.

853
01:10:37,841 --> 01:10:40,032
Thank you.
-Go, please go.

854
01:10:42,177 --> 01:10:43,695
Come here, my lion. Come on!

855
01:10:45,472 --> 01:10:49,231
Come on, well done! Come, come.

856
01:10:52,421 --> 01:10:53,419
I heard that...

857
01:10:54,832 --> 01:10:58,455
...school teacher followed you to Patna.

858
01:10:58,659 --> 01:10:59,995
To nab you.

859
01:11:02,637 --> 01:11:06,218
She has sworn to get you caught.
She's your enemy.

860
01:11:07,181 --> 01:11:10,014
If she gets us caught, she'll die.

861
01:11:10,035 --> 01:11:11,711
She has to die.

862
01:11:12,436 --> 01:11:15,071
You three are lions.

863
01:11:15,371 --> 01:11:16,911
She is after you.

864
01:11:17,324 --> 01:11:20,184
(Laughs)

865
01:11:20,418 --> 01:11:21,822
Don't waste time.

866
01:11:22,822 --> 01:11:25,243
Shoot her on sight.

867
01:11:25,521 --> 01:11:30,490
Before she gets to your neck, kill her.

868
01:11:32,371 --> 01:11:34,835
Go... very good. Go.

869
01:11:43,825 --> 01:11:45,301
The trust has become fund.

870
01:11:46,875 --> 01:11:49,877
I'll meet the minister
after the teacher dies.

871
01:11:51,381 --> 01:11:53,309
I will take back the school contract.

872
01:11:54,425 --> 01:11:55,341
Understood?

873
01:11:56,198 --> 01:11:59,141
I don't give money simply
for minister's elections.

874
01:12:02,299 --> 01:12:05,755
Contract is of no use
if there's no murders.

875
01:12:07,307 --> 01:12:10,719
An animal costs more than
a child in our village.

876
01:12:10,768 --> 01:12:13,648
Sir, 15 children have been sold
from our village.

877
01:12:13,696 --> 01:12:16,735
All this is because of
Raghuveer and Lakhan.

878
01:12:21,161 --> 01:12:23,904
We had taken some loan
from Raghuveer.

879
01:12:24,999 --> 01:12:27,202
He snatched our cattle
and land in return.

880
01:12:27,282 --> 01:12:28,866
He killed my husband too.

881
01:12:42,943 --> 01:12:43,780
I will see.

882
01:13:02,813 --> 01:13:05,707
Avdesh, what are you doing?

883
01:13:07,892 --> 01:13:09,153
Are you supporting Lakhan?

884
01:13:09,693 --> 01:13:11,596
The same Lakhan who killed your father?

885
01:13:12,120 --> 01:13:15,744
This girl, she saved your Poonam.

886
01:13:15,839 --> 01:13:17,369
Will you shoot her?

887
01:13:18,147 --> 01:13:22,333
Come on... kill me... Kill her!

888
01:13:22,623 --> 01:13:26,096
Come on, kill her! Kill me.
Kill everyone in the village.

889
01:13:26,129 --> 01:13:29,675
Come on, shoot.
What are you watching! Come on!

890
01:13:32,593 --> 01:13:34,955
Avdesh, Lakhan is using you.

891
01:13:35,474 --> 01:13:37,420
Surrender yourself to the police.

892
01:13:37,922 --> 01:13:40,600
Nothing will happen to you,
I'll be with you... -Stay back.

893
01:14:04,009 --> 01:14:05,793
If the teacher wasn't there...

894
01:14:06,462 --> 01:14:08,944
...Poonam wouldn't have returned.

895
01:14:12,149 --> 01:14:15,781
Scoundrel Lakhan is manipulating us.

896
01:14:16,414 --> 01:14:19,501
He killed my father,
now he's become my father.

897
01:14:20,185 --> 01:14:22,118
Lakhan must be bad man of this area.

898
01:14:23,462 --> 01:14:26,731
We have killed an ant.
We've killed a rat.

899
01:14:27,049 --> 01:14:28,371
We have killed a snake.

900
01:14:29,078 --> 01:14:30,427
We have killed human too.

901
01:14:30,932 --> 01:14:33,595
Now we'll kill Lakhan.
-How will we kill him?

902
01:14:34,417 --> 01:14:36,723
He comes to the furnace every morning.

903
01:14:39,366 --> 01:14:41,379
Find out whose place is this.

904
01:14:41,647 --> 01:14:43,635
I have to buy it. Understood?
-Okay, boss.

905
01:14:43,677 --> 01:14:46,327
There'll be a highway here...
railway track here.

906
01:14:46,490 --> 01:14:47,583
The value will increase.

907
01:14:47,754 --> 01:14:48,656
(Gunshot)

908
01:14:48,988 --> 01:14:50,881
Did you hear a gunshot?
-There, boss.

909
01:14:53,402 --> 01:14:56,597
Boss, where are you?
-Hey!

910
01:14:56,677 --> 01:14:58,313
Why is he shouting so much?
-Boss!

911
01:14:58,334 --> 01:14:59,649
Boss, where are you?

912
01:14:59,717 --> 01:15:02,313
Boss!
-What's the matter? Who shot?

913
01:15:02,393 --> 01:15:03,818
Those three guys.

914
01:15:04,069 --> 01:15:06,790
Boss, those three guys killed Ravi.

915
01:15:13,354 --> 01:15:17,259
Run, boss!
-Hey, start the car!

916
01:15:17,339 --> 01:15:20,435
Hey, start the car!
-We'll not spare him.

917
01:15:20,515 --> 01:15:23,680
Hey, stop! Stop!
-(Gunshot)

918
01:15:23,760 --> 01:15:27,408
Come on, move, move!

919
01:15:28,134 --> 01:15:29,206
(Gunshot)

920
01:15:31,473 --> 01:15:34,284
Stop! Where are you running? Stop!

921
01:15:35,151 --> 01:15:36,559
Scoundrel!

922
01:15:40,901 --> 01:15:43,486
Balkishan!
-Why did this idiot come here?

923
01:15:43,608 --> 01:15:45,270
Hey Balkishan!
-Oh.

924
01:15:45,716 --> 01:15:47,193
Why are you panting so much?

925
01:15:47,605 --> 01:15:51,303
(Panting)

926
01:15:52,836 --> 01:15:55,793
What's the matter?
-(Panting)

927
01:15:55,873 --> 01:15:57,309
Why are you so tensed?

928
01:15:58,892 --> 01:16:02,854
I got saved. (Panting)
Balkishan, I got saved.

929
01:16:03,507 --> 01:16:07,477
He shot at me.
-You? Who shot at you?

930
01:16:09,855 --> 01:16:15,283
Those... (Panting)
those three guys fired bullet at me.

931
01:16:15,613 --> 01:16:18,682
Those guys fired bullet at you?
-Yes. (Panting)

932
01:16:19,457 --> 01:16:22,121
They were my servants,
but they betrayed me.

933
01:16:23,124 --> 01:16:28,124
Now I have to escape from them
in my own village.

934
01:16:28,867 --> 01:16:32,813
I have to fear them.
Balkishan, do something.

935
01:16:33,071 --> 01:16:35,551
Kill them.
-No, I can't.

936
01:16:36,009 --> 01:16:38,478
SP has ordered us to arrest them.

937
01:16:38,885 --> 01:16:40,449
Is SP superior than me?

938
01:16:40,529 --> 01:16:42,840
Brother, SP is superior.
-Balkishan!

939
01:16:42,935 --> 01:16:45,150
I mean, even you are superior.

940
01:16:45,713 --> 01:16:50,023
Now... this police job is such.

941
01:16:50,666 --> 01:16:52,655
I will find a way.
-No, no.

942
01:16:54,451 --> 01:16:55,759
You don't find a way.

943
01:16:57,504 --> 01:16:59,246
I will find a way myself.

944
01:17:00,840 --> 01:17:02,966
That teacher is acting very smart.

945
01:17:06,334 --> 01:17:09,555
Now I will act smart.

946
01:17:11,626 --> 01:17:15,591
You just sit and watch. Understood?

947
01:17:16,843 --> 01:17:19,366
You'll just watch.
-Okay.

948
01:17:19,766 --> 01:17:22,296
Hey... have something cold at least.

949
01:17:24,288 --> 01:17:25,471
Oh no!

950
01:17:30,754 --> 01:17:32,950
(Bird chirping)

951
01:17:42,859 --> 01:17:44,300
Did you admit Ravi in the hospital?

952
01:17:44,586 --> 01:17:46,381
Boss, Ravi died.

953
01:17:46,461 --> 01:17:50,405
(Grunts)

954
01:17:54,206 --> 01:17:55,691
This is that teacher's doing.

955
01:17:57,498 --> 01:17:59,692
All this happened because of her.

956
01:18:01,070 --> 01:18:02,931
Bhola...
-Yes, boss?

957
01:18:03,165 --> 01:18:04,102
Bhola!

958
01:18:06,261 --> 01:18:10,485
Find her...
find her and get her here.

959
01:18:11,649 --> 01:18:13,716
I will show her who I am.

960
01:18:15,617 --> 01:18:18,747
Until you don't get her, I'll sit here.

961
01:18:19,233 --> 01:18:22,327
I will not move from here. Get her!
-Let's go.

962
01:18:22,407 --> 01:18:24,894
I will not spare that teacher.

963
01:18:25,759 --> 01:18:32,407
"Touch the gem of education
with knowledge."

964
01:18:32,487 --> 01:18:36,488
"Make our lives worth living."

965
01:18:36,568 --> 01:18:40,746
"Make our lives worth living."

966
01:18:42,664 --> 01:18:46,205
Move...
-Hey, move!

967
01:18:55,797 --> 01:18:57,785
Hey, what are you doing?
-Come on!

968
01:18:58,312 --> 01:19:02,407
Leave me! Leave me!
-Hey, move back children!

969
01:19:02,487 --> 01:19:04,420
What are you doing?
-Hey, come on!

970
01:19:04,500 --> 01:19:07,987
Move back! Come on!
-Come on!

971
01:19:08,366 --> 01:19:11,583
Hey Lallan, you get teacher's car.
-Leave me!

972
01:19:11,604 --> 01:19:14,037
Hey...
-Leave me!

973
01:19:14,556 --> 01:19:16,489
Where are you taking me?
-Hey!

974
01:19:18,238 --> 01:19:20,210
(Screaming)

975
01:19:24,813 --> 01:19:26,813
Hold her tightly.

976
01:19:27,188 --> 01:19:29,579
Shut up...
-Sit quietly.

977
01:19:29,600 --> 01:19:32,494
Shut up, don't make any noise.

978
01:19:32,947 --> 01:19:35,835
You are acting very smart.
-Shut up!

979
01:19:35,915 --> 01:19:38,110
Will you mess with us?
-Shut up!

980
01:19:39,921 --> 01:19:42,462
Just sit quietly.

981
01:19:42,907 --> 01:19:47,245
Hold her tightly.
-Hey, hold her.

982
01:19:48,651 --> 01:19:50,665
Don't make any noise.

983
01:20:08,070 --> 01:20:12,095
Greetings... teacher.
-Come on, get down.

984
01:20:12,516 --> 01:20:14,516
Get her here.
-Come on, move.

985
01:20:14,596 --> 01:20:17,203
Hey, come on.
-Boss, here's the teacher.

986
01:20:18,127 --> 01:20:22,416
(Stretching)

987
01:20:28,669 --> 01:20:33,665
Oh city girl...
have you heard that old proverb?

988
01:20:34,063 --> 01:20:39,478
You shouldn't lock horns with
someone living in the same area.

989
01:20:45,972 --> 01:20:49,228
You've come to our area
and sacked me from the job.

990
01:20:51,524 --> 01:20:58,241
Those three guys...
who used to listen to me blindly...

991
01:20:58,986 --> 01:21:00,736
...you turned them against me.

992
01:21:02,951 --> 01:21:06,312
You made them attack me?

993
01:21:06,773 --> 01:21:12,260
Police may be working
for the public in your city.

994
01:21:14,021 --> 01:21:16,217
The law may be working for the public.

995
01:21:18,270 --> 01:21:19,235
But here...

996
01:21:22,034 --> 01:21:25,318
...police works to protect me...

997
01:21:25,868 --> 01:21:29,446
...and law also works to protect me.

998
01:21:30,087 --> 01:21:31,134
Understood?

999
01:21:32,195 --> 01:21:37,546
Look, no matter
what I do with you here...

1000
01:21:39,069 --> 01:21:44,571
...neither law nor the police
will harm me.

1001
01:21:47,390 --> 01:21:52,075
I will harm you.

1002
01:21:53,657 --> 01:21:54,462
(Slaps)

1003
01:22:01,399 --> 01:22:04,431
This is the punishment
for sacking me from the job.

1004
01:22:05,731 --> 01:22:06,434
(Slaps)

1005
01:22:09,123 --> 01:22:11,963
(Laughs)

